data.description: This newly built Centex home is ready for its next homeowner. This 2-story luxury home features a spacious kitchen and great room. The downstairs guest bedroom and bathroom gives great flexibility to this home. A large upstairs game room offers the perfect space for entertainment. Also, the primary bedroom features a separate garden tub and stand in shower in the owner's suite.
